entries.journal_entry_description: Manfred wants you to kill the Chiss poachers' leader.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Manfred wants you to kill the Chiss poachers' leader, Laen Pieweto.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Laen Pieweto is dead. Let Manfred know of your success. He's at the main Rodian hunting camp.
